ESP32 SD READER

Copyright: (c) 2026 Erilov Nikita

This project is an ESP32-S3 firmware for reading SD card metadata,
including CID, manufacturer information, serial number, manufacturing
date, capacity, used space, and free space.

Third-party components:
  - ESP-IDF by Espressif Systems
  - espressif/led_strip component by Espressif Systems

Third-party components are distributed under their respective licenses.
